# Additional execution notes (for the agent carrying this out)
- Follow the exact prior execution pattern from refactor-hadacard.2 (review as hard gate, programme with [[phase]], etc.).
- Authorized changes will be listed in the review only.
- Make the button "special": not a plain BackButton copy — give it card-specific presence (perhaps a very subtle foil or just perfect aero + the exact color/rounding/shadow language the card uses).
- "transitions it landscape": the whole holo-card changes aspect and internal layout live with CSS transitions; content doesn't jump.
- Cool new way: the new content (scrollMsg banner + P.S.) should use the same animation primitives (letter-block, revealUp, etc.) and feel like they were always part of the letter, just hidden until you "opened it wide".
- After impl: update the .programme progress, append rich log, write history that celebrates the craft.